    "long_instructions": "##  🔍Teacher Tip\r\nStudents will see each of these levels separately. We've combined here them for a more streamlined PL experience. \r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Sports Journalist - Minimal Context Given\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a sports journalist by giving a simple, unstructured prompt to see how AI responds without any examples or extra details.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Try a basic prompt like the one below, or a similar one related to breaking news.\r\n\r\n>Summarize the latest sports news.\r\n\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how much detail the AI includes and how clear or vague the summary is.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Sports Journalist - Providing a Single Example\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a sports journalist by adding a single example to help guide the AI's response.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Prompt AI for a news summary by including **an example** to help the AI understand what you're looking for. \r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how the example affects the tone, structure, or detail in the summary.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure where to start?**]\r\nHere's an example prompt:\r\n> Summarize the latest sports news as a series of 1-sentence summaries. For example:\r\n>\r\n> \"Alabama wins over Texas Tech in nailbiter game.\" \r\n:::\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Sports Journalist - Providing Multiple Examples\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a sports journalist by giving the AI more structure and detailed expectations to guide a stronger response.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Prompt AI for a news summary by including **several examples** to help the AI understand what you're looking for. \r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how adding structure and specific details improved the AI’s summary.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure where to start?**]\r\nHere's an example prompt:\r\n> Summarize the latest sports news as a series of 1-sentence summaries. For example:\r\n>\r\n> \"Alabama wins over Texas Tech in nailbiter game.\" \r\n> \"Caitlin Clark autograph card sells for a record $84,000.\"\r\n> \"Stefon Diggs could transform the Patriots offense from the slot position.\"\r\n:::",
